ecshospital

Interface Customizable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Doctors, Health, HospitalAdministrator, LimbSurgeon, OrganSurgeon, Patient, Person, Surgeon

    public interface Customizable
    The are values and properties that are customizable in the ECS hospital, new properties could be imported from the configuration file.

    However, if the setting (E.g. modify recovery time) has a syntax error, the program will ignore the new configuration and continue the use of the default setting.

    Man-Leong Chan
